casebody.data:
Thursday, July 30, 1992

MERIT DOCKET

92-1466. State ex rel. Russell v. Shaker Hts. Mun. Court.

In Prohibition. This cause originated in this court on the filing of a complaint for a writ of prohibition and was considered in a manner prescribed by law. Upon consideration thereof,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that said writ of prohibition be, and the same is hereby, denied, effective July 29, 1992.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur. Douglas, J., would dismiss.
